The paper presents a new Python library for machine learning with time series data, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-fields of computer science. However, the focus of the paper is on the design of the library's core API and its support for various time series tasks and reduction approaches, which suggests a strong emphasis on machine learning and data science (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions time series classification and forecasting, which are tasks that are often tackled using computer vision techniques (cs.CV) or signal processing methods (cs.SI).
